response.original_title: The Best of Country Music from Ireland
response.overview: 'The Best Of Country Music From Ireland' contains tracks by Susan McCann, Gene Stuart, Philomen Begley, Gloria, Frank McCaffrey and Crawford Bell. Tracks include 'Someone is Looking', 'I'm Just Lucky I Guess', 'The Way Old Friends Do', 'Brady From Strabane', 'Country Memories', 'Isle of Innisfree', 'Everybody's Somebody's Fool', 'One Day At A Time', 'God's Colouring Book', 'More Than Yesterday', 'The Sunny Side of The Mountain' and 'Seven Spanish Angels'.
response.title: The Best of Country Music from Ireland
